---

<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 max-w-screen-xl text-center lg:mt-40 lg:p-8"
>
  <h1
    class="my-8 font-header text-3xl font-bold md:text-3xl lg:text-6xl"
    id="about_us"
  >
    “So, what is it that you folks do at Bitshala?”
  </h1>

  <p class="m-4 hidden text-lg md:block lg:text-2xl">
    Bitshala is a <span class="font-bold text-orange"
      >grassroots education initiative</span
    > led by Indian Bitcoiners, focused on strengthening the
    Bitcoin <br /> ecosystem by <span
      class="font-bold text-orange"
      >nurturing and supporting Bitcoin FOSS (Free and Open
      Source Software) Devs</span
    >. Our mission <br /> is to equip people with the skills
    and knowledge needed to contribute to Bitcoin FOSS
    projects.
    <br /> We want you to be part of the revolution.
  </p>

  <p
    class="text-lgmd:text-lg m-4 block md:hidden lg:text-2xl"
  >
    Bitshala is a <span class="font-bold text-orange"
      >grassroots education initiative <br /></span
    > led by Indian Bitcoiners, focused on <br />
     strengthening the Bitcoin ecosystem by <br />
    <span class="font-bold text-orange"
      >nurturing and supporting Bitcoin FOSS <br /> (Free
      and Open Source Software) Devs</span
    >. <br /> Our mission is to equip people with the <br />
     skills and knowledge needed to contribute <br /> to
    Bitcoin FOSS projects.
    <br /> We want you to be part of the revolution.
  </p>

  <div
    class="m-5 flex flex-col rounded-3xl border-2 border-black border-opacity-5 bg-peach lg:m-0 lg:mb-8 lg:mt-48 lg:flex-row"
  >
    <h1
      class="my-3 ml-3 text-center font-header lg:my-8 lg:w-2/3 lg:pl-3 lg:text-start lg:text-3xl"
    >
      Trusted and Supported by
    </h1>
    <div
      class="mx-auto flex items-center gap-6 pl-5 pr-10 lg:w-[120%] lg:justify-end lg:gap-10"
    >
      {
        trustedList.map((li) => (
          <a href={li.link}>
            <img
              src={li.link}
              class="h-8 object-contain py-2 lg:h-16"
              alt="Bitshala Logo"
            />
          </a>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="m-5 flex flex-col rounded-3xl border-2 border-black border-opacity-5 bg-peach lg:m-0 lg:mb-32 lg:flex-row"
  >
    <h1
      class="t my-3 ml-3 text-center font-header lg:my-8 lg:w-2/3 lg:pl-3 lg:text-start lg:text-3xl"
    >
      In collaboration with
    </h1>
    <div
      class="mx-auto flex items-center gap-6 pr-5 lg:w-[120%] lg:justify-end lg:gap-10"
    >
      {
        colabList.map((li) => (
          <a href={li.link}>
            <img
              src={li.link}
              class="h-8 object-contain py-2 lg:h-16"
              alt="Bitshala Logo"
            />
          </a>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>

